data.description: Better than brand new, this move-in ready 3 bedrooms & 2.5 bathrooms Granada model home by DR Horton features a private, fenced corner lot with a hot tub in the screened-in lanai. The spacious kitchen, with eat-in nook, has beautiful granite counters & breakfast bar. Only a year old, the stainless steel appliances are still under warranty. The upgraded master bedroom boasts a tray ceiling, bay windows, double walk-in closets with a master bath that includes Garden tub, extended vanity with double sinks, walk-in shower, and private commode. Washer & dryer are included. Located in the premier golf course community of Venetian Bay, with miles of walking & biking trails, town center, restaurants, Beach & Swim Club, fitness center & Day School for preschoolers with after-school programs.
